text: Kurama () is a rural locality (a village) in Tungatarovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 505 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 50 km from Uchaly, 5 km from Komsomolsk. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Kurama, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
